[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    297[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ### N1. The dead-code path in `_handle_benefits_message` for `REQUIRE_AUTHENTICATED_FOR_MEMBER_SPECIFIC` does nothing; the comment explains the behavior is delegated to `_classify_and_route`, but the `if/pass` is a no-op that only confuses readers
